data.title: Six on Stage - Who's who at the Eurovision Song Contest
data.meta_description: Performers who have represented Finland at the Eurovision Song Contest.
data.text:
Finland

Performers who have represented Finland at the Eurovision Song Contest.

Finland first participated in 1961 and made its most recent appearance in 2024. It has won the Contest once.
